{"tid":1558552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[18區] 旺角MOKO大合唱 (再黎) 9月11 星期三","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T18:55:03.000Z","uid":164420,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40f8999a02ed6d17b364a2aca55ab00c9f3e80b9","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"上個post唔夠人，因為撞正大球場賽事，好多巴打未能趕回MK。而家再搞過！同時鼓勵其他區既商場都一齊搞，效果會更好！<br />\n<br />\n太古城班中產都唱左，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">MK仔女點可以落後於人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月11星期三晚上9:00</span></span>，全體MK街坊集合moko各層一齊大合唱 &lt;願榮光歸香港&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港 Glory To Hong Kong》<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\nFor all of our tears on our land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\nDo you feel the rage in our cries?<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\nRise up and speak up! Our voice echoes<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\nFreedom shall shine upon us<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\nFor all of our fear that lingers<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\nWith faith, we shall never surrender<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\nWith blood, tears and sweat, we shall stride ahead<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\nFor this glory, lib-eral land<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\nWhen the stars no longer guide our path<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\nIn the fog, the horn of conscience summon us<br />\n&quot;捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n&ldquo;Persevere! For we are as one, with poise and be brave<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot;<br />\nCourage, wisdom, are long with us.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\nThe dawn has come. Let&rsquo;s revive our Hong Kong<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\nRevolution of our time! For righteousness!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\nDemocracy, n&rsquo;liberty, wish them long last here<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\nFor the glory of Hong Kong"},{"pid":"a2361cd01ed3376cc110ec999056ea102fc19f89","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d6141f19e6eef37709be03e8b5b4a541f57ca0b5","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"2/10 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b645d6e5b3283411291837b1e43ffa7a53e14b","tid":1558552,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93f161cfce200119259c8c94b5d5b7dcfaf338fd","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d131c131760a099e0297970fdc8777c03b0ef90a","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"4/10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62f323e8fc89a4accc1449c0ea303141485fe2b","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"5/10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43525cec880689f73efbd76abc1e0e112f70cac6","tid":1558552,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"6/10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr